:: Arcade [nobr location]
<<set $gamelocation to "Arcade">>
You enter a large arcade. Lined from wall to wall are all sorts of video games, some retro, some modern, and some next generation.

<br>
Unfortunately a astral barrier blocks the way forward, with the words "THIS AREA IS A WORK IN PROGESS"
